arStrings.szText: An old drunk, the judge of what is real? (laughter) We are real, and so is the law of the swamp.
Referencing a line from Lorath where he talks to himself and says "You aren't real," trying to quiet the voices in his head.
To get the answers you seek, you must offer payment. A head for knowledge.
Not yet. They have another purpose first.
Reference to the heads thinking Player and team can help them track down Elias, the character who betrayed the Tree of Whispers.
